            "🫦 {user} used a single look to promise the Master a lifetime of pleasure. Earned **{reward}** Flames.",
            "🫦 {user} teased the audience by slowly removing a single, ornate stocking. Earned **{reward}** Flames.",
            "🫦 {user} promised to kneel only for the Master but teased every guard in the wing. Earned **{reward}** Flames.",
            "🫦 {user} performed a 'Silent Siren' show while completely naked and bound. Earned **{reward}** Flames.",
